 
 How to compile OnionMail:
 
 1) Downlaod the complete JAVA SE 7.1 library with patch.
 	This enables the all modes SSL. There are some limitations. 
        JAVA SSL BUG: JDK-7044060 Update your JDK!
        This may be a NSA's limitation.
        
 2) Replace the content of jce_policy-6.zip in your JDK library.
 	Remove some USA & NSA's limitations.

 3) Add some bouncy Castle libray jars:
	bcprov-ext-jdk15on-149.jar
	bcpg-jdk15on-150.jar
	 
